description: Under normal circumstances, the fund primarily invests in equity securities, focusing on growth equity securities. Under normal circumstances, it invests at least 40% of its net assets in foreign and emerging market securities. The fund invests in equity securities of different market capitalizations (small, medium, or large). The fund will concentrate its investments (invest more than 25% of its assets) in one or more industries within the consumer discretionary sector and one or more industries within the communication services sector.
name: Principal Millennial Global Growth ETF
